AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080125 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'sound insulation index' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'acoustic capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080125 "AcousticCapability(x) ← SoundInsulationIndex(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080125 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
