# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080127 (electrical capacitance)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ElectricalCapacitance>

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080127 "electrical capacitance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080127 "elektrische Kapazität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080127 "electrical capacity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080127 "elektrische Kapazität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080127 "ElectricalCapability(x) ← ElectricalCapacitance(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080127 "electrical capacitance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080127 "Electrical capacitance refers to an entity's ability to store electric charge, expressed as the amount of electric charge stored per given electric potential"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080127 "Die elektrische Kapazität bezieht sich auf die Fähigkeit eines Wesens, elektrische Ladung zu speichern, ausgedrückt als die Menge an elektrischer Ladung, die pro gegebenem elektrischem Potenzial gespeichert wird"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080127 "A ceramic capacitor has an electrical capacitance of 100 nF, storing charge in an electronic circuit"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080127 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'electrical capacitance' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'electrical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080127 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080127 pmdco:PMD_0080126)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080128 (electrical resistance)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ElectricalResistance>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080128 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'electrical resistance' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'electrical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://www.britannica.com/technology/resistance-electronics."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080128 <https://www.britannica.com/technology/resistance-electronics>)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080128 "Electrical resistance pertains to a circuit's capability to transform electric energy into heat energy, opposing electric current through particle collisions, characteristic of resistors, lamps, and wires"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080128 "Der elektrische Widerstand bezieht sich auf die Fähigkeit eines Stromkreises, elektrische Energie in Wärmeenergie umzuwandeln, indem er elektrischem Strom durch Teilchenkollisionen entgegenwirkt, die für Widerstände, Lampen und Drähte charakteristisch sind"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080128 "elektrischer Widerstand"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080128 "electrical resistance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080128 "ElectricalCapability(x) ← ElectricalResistance(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080128 "A nichrome heating element has an electrical resistance of 10 Ω at room temperature"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080128 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080128 pmdco:PMD_0080126)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080129 (electrical conductance)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ElectricalConductance>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080129 "ElectricalCapability(x) ← ElectricalConductance(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080129 "Stromleitwert"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080129 "elektrischer Leitwert"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080129 "electrical conductance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080129 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'electrical conductance' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'electrical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080129 "Der elektrische Leitwert stellt den Kehrwert des elektrischen Widerstands eines Leiters dar und misst seine Fähigkeit, elektrischen Strom zu leiten, angegeben in Siemens (S)."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080129 "Electrical conductance represents the reciprocal of a conductor's electrical resistance, measuring its ability to conduct an electric current, denoted in siemens (S)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080129 "elektrischer Leitwert"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080129 "electrical conductance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080129 "A copper wire of 1 m length and 1 mm2 cross-section has an electrical conductance of about 59 S"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080129 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080129 pmdco:PMD_0080126)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080130 (magnetic capability)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/MagneticCapability>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080130 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'magnetic capability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080130 "PhysicalCapability(x) ← MagneticCapability(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080130 "Magnetic capability is a physical capability of a material that can be realized through interactions involving magnetic fields or magnetic ordering"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080130 "Magnetische Fähigkeit ist eine physische Fähigkeit eines Materials, die durch Wechselwirkungen mit Magnetfeldern oder magnetischer Ordnung realisiert werden kann"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080130 "magnetic capability"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080130 "magnetische Fähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080130 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080130 obo:BFO_0000016)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080131 (saturation magnetization)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/SaturationMagnetization>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080131 "Sättigungsmagnetisierung ist eine magnetische Fähigkeit eines Materials, die das maximale magnetische Moment pro Volumeneinheit angibt, das erreicht wird, wenn alle magnetischen Domänen mit einem angelegten äußeren Feld ausgerichtet sind"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080131 "Saturation magnetization is a magnetic capability of a material that specifies the maximum magnetic moment per unit volume achieved when all magnetic domains are aligned with an applied external field"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080131 "magnetische Sättigung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080131 "magnetic saturation"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080131 "MagneticCapability(x) ← SaturationMagnetization(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080131 "Sättigungsmagnetisierung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080131 "saturation magnetization"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080131 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'saturation magnetization' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'magnetic capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080131 "M_s"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080131 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080131 pmdco:PMD_0080130)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080132 (mechanical capability)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/MechanicalCapability>

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080132 "mechanische Fähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080132 "mechanical capability"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080132 "Mechanische Fähigkeiten können durch eine Entität realisiert werden, die mit mechanischer Interaktion zusammenhängt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080132 "Mechanical capability can be realized through an entity related to mechanical interaction"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080132 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'mechanical capability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080132 "A spring steel coil spring has the mechanical capability to store 50 J of elastic energy per cycle"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080132 "PhysicalCapability(x) ← MechanicalCapability(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080132 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080132 obo:BFO_0000016)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080133 (durability)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/Durability>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080133 "durability"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080133 "Dauerhaftigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080133 "Langlebigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080133 "longevity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080133 "MechanicalCapability(x) ← Durability(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080133 "Durability is the ability of a material to resist wear, tear, and other types of damage over time"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080133 "Die Dauerhaftigkeit ist die Fähigkeit eines Materials, Abnutzung, Rissbildung und andere Arten von Schäden im Laufe der Zeit zu widerstehen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080133 "Galvanized steel shows high durability in outdoor environments, resisting corrosion for over 50 years"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080133 "durability"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080133 "Dauerhaftigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080133 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'durability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'mechanical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080133 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080133 pmdco:PMD_0080132)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080134 (wear resistance)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/WearResistance>

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080134 "Verschleißfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080134 "wear resistance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080134 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'wear resistance' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'durability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080134 "resistance to wear"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080134 "widerstand gegen Verschleiß"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080134 "Verschleißfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080134 "wear resistance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080134 "Hardened tool steel has high wear resistance, maintaining a cutting edge through thousands of machining cycles"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080134 "Verschleißfestigkeit ist die Fähigkeit eines Materials, mechanischen Aktionen wie Reiben, Kratzen oder Erosion zu widerstehen, die dazu tendieren, Material allmählich von seiner Oberfläche zu entfernen."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080134 "Wear resistance is the ability of a material to resist mechanical actions such as rubbing, scraping or erosion that tend to progressively remove material from its surface."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080134 "Durability(x) ← WearResistance(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080134 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080134 pmdco:PMD_0080133)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080135 (creep resistance)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/CreepResistance>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Creep Resistance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Kriechfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Creep Resistant"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Kriechfestig"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Kriechfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080135 "creep resistance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Die Kriechfestigkeit ist die Fähigkeit eines Materials, unter Last über einen bestimmten Zeitraum eine Deformation zu widerstehen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Creep resistance is the ability of a material to resist deformation under load over time"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'creep resistance' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'durability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Durability(x) ← CreepResistance(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080135 "Nickel superalloys have high creep resistance, maintaining shape under stress at 1000 C in turbine blades"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080135 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080135 pmdco:PMD_0080133)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080136 (poisson effect)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/PoissonEffect>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080136 "Was a subclass of 'Mechanical Quality'")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080136 "Poisson effect describes deformation perpendicular to the direction of loading, named after Siméon Poisson"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080136 "Querkontraktion beschreibt die Deformation senkrecht zur Belastungsrichtung, benannt nach Siméon Poisson"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080136 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poisson%27s_ratio>)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080136 "MechanicalCapability(x) ← PoissonEffect(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080136 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'poisson effect' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'mechanical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poisson%27s_ratio."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080136 "A rubber cylinder loaded axially expands radially due to the Poisson effect, with a ratio of about 0.5"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080136 "Querkontraktion"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080136 "poisson effect"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080136 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080136 pmdco:PMD_0080132)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080137 (poisson's ratio)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/PoissonRatio>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080137 "Poissonzahl ist ein Maß für den Poisson-Effekt, mit Werten typischerweise zwischen 0,0 und 0,5 für die meisten Materialien"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080137 "Poisson's ratio is a measure of the Poisson effect, with values typically between 0.0 and 0.5 for most materials"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080137 "Poissonzahl"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080137 "poisson's ratio"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080137 "PoissonEffect(x) ← PoissonRatio(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080137 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'poisson's ratio' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'poisson effect'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poisson%27s_ratio."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080137 "Rubber has a Poisson's ratio close to 0.5, indicating nearly incompressible behavior under loading"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080137 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poisson%27s_ratio>)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080137 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080137 pmdco:PMD_0080136)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080138 (material fatigue)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/MaterialFatigue>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080138 "Material fatigue is the failure of a material caused by repeated or sustained loading below its ultimate strength."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080138 "Materialermüdung ist das Versagen von Werkstoffen infolge wiederholter oder dauernder Belastung unterhalb der Probenfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080138 "fatigue of material"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080138 "Ermüdung des Materials"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080138 "material fatigue"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080138 "Materialermüdung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080138 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'aterial fatigue' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'mechanical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080138 "MechanicalCapability(x) ← MaterialFatigue(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080138 "Repeated cyclic loading at 400 MPa induces material fatigue in a steel shaft, leading to crack initiation"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080138 "material fatigue"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080138 "Materialermüdung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080138 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080138 pmdco:PMD_0080132)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080139 (impact energy)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ImpactEnergy>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080139 "Impact energy is a mechanical capability of a material that characterises the total energy absorbed by a standardised notched specimen during fracture under a single impact blow, as measured in a Charpy or Izod test"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080139 "Schlagenergie ist eine mechanische Fähigkeit eines Materials, die die gesamte Energie beschreibt, die eine standardisierte gekerbte Probe beim Bruch unter einem einzigen Schlagimpuls absorbiert, gemessen im Charpy- oder Izod-Versuch"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080139 "Schlagenergie"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080139 "impact energy"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080139 "Kerbschlagenergie"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080139 "Charpy impact energy"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080139 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'impact energy' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'mechanical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080139 "KV"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080139 "MechanicalCapability(x) ← ImpactEnergy(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080139 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080139 pmdco:PMD_0080132)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080140 (hardness)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/Hardness>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080140 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'hardness' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080140 "hardness"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080140 "Härte"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080140 "Strength(x) ← Hardness(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080140 "Härte ist die Widerstandsfähigkeit eines Materials gegen lokalisierte Verformung oder Plastizität, die durch mechanische Einwirkung wie Biegen, Quetschen oder Kratzen verursacht wird"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080140 "Hardness quantifies the resistance of a material to localized deformation or plasticity caused by mechanical action, such as bending, crushing, or scratching"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080140 "hardness"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080140 "Härte"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080140 "Hardened bearing steel achieves a hardness of 62 HRC after quench and tempering"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080140 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080140 pmdco:PMD_0000952)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080141 (indentation hardness)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/IndentationHardness>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080141 "Hardness(x) ← IndentationHardness(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080141 "Indentation hardness is a measure of a material's resistance to indentation"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080141 "Indentationshärte ist ein Maß für die Widerstandsfähigkeit eines Materials gegen Eindringen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080141 "identation hardness"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080141 "Indentationshärte"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080141 "Indentationshärte"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080141 "indentation hardness"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080141 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'indentation hardness' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'hardness'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080141 "Was a subclass of 'Hardness'")
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080141 "The indentation hardness of a polymer measured by the Shore D scale is 75, indicating semi-rigid behavior"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080141 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080141 pmdco:PMD_0080140)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080142 (scratch hardness)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ScratchHardness>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080142 "Kratzhärte misst die Fähigkeit eines Materials, Kratzern zu widerstehen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080142 "Scratch hardness measures a material's ability to resist being scratched"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080142 "Kratzbeständigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080142 "scratch resistance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080142 "Hardness(x) ← ScratchHardness(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080142 "Kratzhärte"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080142 "scratch hardness"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080142 "A mineral with a scratch hardness of 7 on the Mohs scale scratches glass but not topaz"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080142 "scratch hardness"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080142 "Kratzfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080142 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'scratch hardness' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'hardness'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080142 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080142 pmdco:PMD_0080140)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080143 (viscoelasticity)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/Viscoelasticity>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080143 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'viscoelasticity' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080143 "Viscoelastizität beschreibt Materialien, die sowohl viskose als auch elastische Eigenschaften während der Verformung zeigen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080143 "Viscoelasticity describes materials exhibiting both viscous and elastic characteristics during deformation"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080143 "Polymers exhibit viscoelasticity, showing both elastic recovery and creep under constant load"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080143 "viscoelasticity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080143 "Viscoelastizität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080143 "Viscoelastizität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080143 "viscoelasticity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080143 "elasticity of viscosity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080143 "Viskoelastizität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080143 "Strength(x) ← Viscoelasticity(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080143 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080143 pmdco:PMD_0000952)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080144 (creep modulus)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/CreepModulus>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080144 "Creep modulus measures a material's viscoelasticity, indicating its ability to deform under stress over time"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080144 "Der Kriechmodul ist ein Maß für die Viskoelastizität eines Materials, das seine Fähigkeit zur Verformung unter Belastung im Laufe der Zeit beschreibt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080144 "creep modulus"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080144 "Kriechmodul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080144 "Viscoelasticity(x) ← CreepModulus(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080144 "creep modulus"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080144 "Kriechmodul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080144 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'creep modulus' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'viscoelasticity'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080144 "The creep modulus of polyethylene at 50 C and 1 MPa after 1000 hours is 200 MPa"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080144 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080144 pmdco:PMD_0080143)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080145 (complex modulus)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ComplexModulus>

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080145 "complex modulus"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080145 "Komplexmodul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080145 "Komplexmodul ist eine viskoelastische Qualität eines Materials, die die gesamte Steifigkeitsantwort unter schwingender Belastung als komplexe Zahl darstellt, bestehend aus dem Speichermodul als Realteil und dem Verlustmodul als Imaginärteil"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080145 "Complex modulus is a viscoelastic quality of a material that represents the total stiffness response under oscillatory loading as a complex number, comprising the storage modulus as the real part and the loss modulus as the imaginary part"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080145 "Viscoelasticity(x) ← ComplexModulus(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080145 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'complex modulus' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'viscoelasticity'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080145 "E*"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080145 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080145 pmdco:PMD_0080143)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080146 (loss modulus)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/LossModulus>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080146 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'loss modulus' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'complex modulus'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_modulus."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080146 "Loss modulus is the imaginary part of the complex modulus that measures the viscous portion of energy dissipated as heat per cycle in a viscoelastic material under oscillatory loading"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080146 "Verlustmodul ist der Imaginärteil des Komplexmoduls und misst den viskosen Anteil der pro Zyklus als Wärme dissipierten Energie in einem viskoelastischen Material unter schwingender Belastung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080146 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_modulus>)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080146 "E''"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080146 "Verlustmodul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080146 "loss modulus"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080146 "ComplexModulus(x) ← LossModulus(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080146 "The loss modulus of a viscoelastic polymer at 1 Hz is 0.3 MPa, representing energy dissipation per cycle"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080146 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080146 pmdco:PMD_0080145)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080147 (dynamic modulus)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/DynamicModulus>

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080147 "dynamic modulus"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080147 "dynamischer Modul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080147 "The dynamic modulus of a rubber compound at 10 Hz is 15 MPa, relevant for vibration isolation design"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080147 "complex shear modulus"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080147 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_modulus>)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080147 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'dynamic modulus' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'complex modulus'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_modulus."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080147 "Dynamischer Modul ist das Verhältnis von Spannung zu Dehnung unter schwingenden Bedingungen, typischerweise gemessen in Scher-, Druck- oder Dehnungstests, und charakterisiert viskoelastische Materialien"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080147 "Dynamic modulus is the ratio of stress to strain under vibratory conditions, typically measured in shear, compression, or elongation tests, and characterizes viscoelastic materials"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080147 "ComplexModulus(x) ← DynamicModulus(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080147 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080147 pmdco:PMD_0080145)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080148 (loss tangent)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/LossTangent>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080148 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_modulus>)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080148 "DynamicModulus(x) ← LossTangent(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080148 "loss tangent"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080148 "Verlustwinkel"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080148 "Loss tangent, represented as tan δ, is the ratio of the loss modulus to storage modulus in viscoelastic materials, providing a measure of damping"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080148 "Der Verlustfaktor, dargestellt als tan δ, ist das Verhältnis des Verlustmoduls zum Speichermodul in viskoelastischen Materialien und liefert ein Maß für die Dämpfung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080148 "A PTFE cable insulator has a loss tangent of 0.0002 at 1 GHz, minimizing signal attenuation"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080148 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'loss tangent' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'dynamic modulus'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_modulus."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080148 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080148 pmdco:PMD_0080147)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080149 (storage modulus)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/StorageModulus>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080149 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_modulus>)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080149 "Speichermodul ist der Realteil des Komplexmoduls und misst den elastischen Anteil der gespeicherten und zurückgewonnenen Energie pro Zyklus in einem viskoelastischen Material unter schwingender Belastung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080149 "Storage modulus is the real part of the complex modulus that measures the elastic portion of energy stored and recovered per cycle in a viscoelastic material under oscillatory loading"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080149 "The storage modulus of a polyurethane foam at 1 Hz and 25 C is 0.5 MPa, reflecting its elastic stiffness"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080149 "E'"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080149 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'storage modulus' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'complex modulus'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_modulus."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080149 "ComplexModulus(x) ← StorageModulus(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080149 "Speichermodul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080149 "storage modulus"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080149 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080149 pmdco:PMD_0080145)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080150 (toughness)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/Toughness>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080150 "Zähigkeit beschreibt die Widerstandsfähigkeit eines Werkstoffs gegen Bruch oder Rissausbreitung, bestimmt durch die Fähigkeit zur Absorption von mechanischer Energie bei Verformung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080150 "Toughness describes the resistance of a material to fracture or crack propagation, determined by its ability to absorb mechanical energy during deformation"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080150 "High-toughness tool steel absorbs 80 J before fracture in a Charpy V-notch test at room temperature"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080150 "Strength(x) ← Toughness(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080150 "Zähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080150 "toughness"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080150 "Zähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080150 "toughness"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080150 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'toughness' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080150 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080150 pmdco:PMD_0000952)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080151 (fracture toughness)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/FractureToughness>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080151 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'fracture toughness' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'toughness'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080151 "Fracture toughness of a high-strength steel measured as 50 MPa·√m according to ISO 17281 test conditions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080151 "fracture toughness"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080151 "Bruchzähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080151 "K_Ic"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080151 "Bruchzähigkeit ist eine Zähigkeitsqualität eines Materials, die die kritische Spannungsintensität beschreibt, bei der ein vorhandener Riss zu wachsen beginnt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080151 "Fracture toughness is a toughness quality of a material that specifies the critical stress intensity at which a pre-existing crack begins to propagate, expressed as the stress intensity factor at the onset of fracture"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080151 "Toughness(x) ← FractureToughness(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080151 "critical stress intensity factor"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080151 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080151 pmdco:PMD_0080150)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080152 (impact strength)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ImpactStrength>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080152 "Schlagfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080152 "mpact strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080152 "Schlagzähigkeit bezeichnet die Fähigkeit eines Materials, Energie zu absorbieren und bei Anwendung einer dynamischen Last plastisch zu verformen, ohne dass es bricht"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080152 "Impact strength is the ability of a material to absorb energy and plastically deform without fracturing under dynamic load"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080152 "Schlagzähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080152 "impact strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080152 "Toughness(x) ← ImpactStrength(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080152 "impact strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080152 "Schlagzähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080152 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'impact strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'toughness'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080152 "A Charpy impact test on notched steel gives an impact strength of 120 J, indicating good toughness"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080152 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080152 pmdco:PMD_0080150)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080153 (breaking strength)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/BreakingStrength>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080153 "Breaking strength is a toughness quality of a specimen that denotes the stress at which the specimen fails via fracture, recorded as the final point on a stress-strain curve"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080153 "Die Bruchfestigkeit ist eine Zähigkeitsqualität einer Probe, die die Spannung angibt, bei der die Probe durch Bruch versagt, aufgezeichnet als Endpunkt auf einer Spannungs-Dehnungs-Kurve"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080153 "stress at break"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080153 "fracture stress"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080153 "Bruchspannung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080153 "strength at break"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080153 "BreakingStrength(x) ↔ Toughness(x) ∧ ∃b∃p∃i(obo:BFO_0000040(b) ∧ MeasurementProcess(p) ∧ MeasurementInformationContentEntity(i) ∧ bearerOf(b, x) ∧ describes(i, x) ∧ isOutputOf(i, p) ∧ ∃t(TimeOfBreak(t) ∧ occupiesTemporalRegion(p, t)))"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080153 "A carbon fiber tow fractures at a breaking strength of 4900 MPa in a tensile test"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080153 "Bruchfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080153 "breaking strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080153 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fracture>)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080153 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080153 pmdco:PMD_0080150)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080154 (tensile strength)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/TensileStrength>

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080154 "Zugfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080154 "tensile strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080154 "BreakingStrength(x) ← TensileStrength(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080154 "Zugfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080154 "ultimate tensile strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080154 "Tensile strength measures the maximum stress a material can withstand while being stretched or pulled before breaking"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080154 "Zugfestigkeit misst die maximale Spannung, die ein Material aushalten kann, während es gestreckt oder gezogen wird, bevor es bricht"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080154 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'tensile strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'breaking strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080154 "A high-strength bolt grade 10.9 has a tensile strength of at least 1040 MPa"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080154 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080154 pmdco:PMD_0080153)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080155 (compressive strength)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/CompressiveStrength>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080155 "Compressive strength of a concrete specimen measured as 30 MPa according to ISO 4012 test conditions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080155 "Druckfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080155 "compressive strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080155 "BreakingStrength(x) ← CompressiveStrength(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080155 "Compressive strength is the maximum stress a material can withstand under uniaxial compressive loading before failure"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080155 "Druckfestigkeit ist die maximale Spannung, die ein Material unter einachsiger Druckbelastung vor dem Versagen widerstehen kann"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080155 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'compressive strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'breaking strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080155 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080155 pmdco:PMD_0080153)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080156 (flexural strength)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/FlexuralStrength>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080156 "flexural strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080156 "Biegefestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080156 "Flexural strength indicates a material's ability to resist deformation under flexural load"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080156 "Biegefestigkeit bezeichnet die Fähigkeit eines Materials, unter Biegelast Deformationen zu widerstehen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080156 "BreakingStrength(x) ← FlexuralStrength(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080156 "flexural strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080156 "Biegefestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080156 "bending strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080156 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'flexural strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'breaking strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080156 "A ceramic bending bar fractures at a flexural strength of 350 MPa in a three-point bend test"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080156 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080156 pmdco:PMD_0080153)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080157 (shear strength)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ShearStrength>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080157 "shear breaking strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080157 "Shear strength is the maximum shear stress a material can withstand before failure along a plane parallel to the applied force"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080157 "Scherfestigkeit ist die maximale Scherspannung, die ein Material entlang einer zur aufgebrachten Kraft parallelen Ebene vor dem Versagen widerstehen kann"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080157 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'shear strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'breaking strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080157 "Shear strength of a CFRP laminate specimen measured as 85 MPa according to ISO 14130 test conditions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080157 "Scherfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080157 "shear strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080157 "BreakingStrength(x) ← ShearStrength(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080157 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080157 pmdco:PMD_0080153)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080158 (operational strength)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/OperationalStrength>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080158 "operational strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080158 "Betriebsfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080158 "Strength(x) ← OperationalStrength(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080158 "Betriebsfestigkeit beschreibt die Fähigkeit eines Systems, seine vorgesehene Funktion in einer betrieblichen Umgebung auszuführen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080158 "Operational strength describes a system's ability to perform its intended function in an operational environment"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080158 "Betriebsstärke"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080158 "operation strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080158 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'operational strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080158 "The operational strength of a drive shaft is the maximum cyclic stress it sustains without fatigue failure in service"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080158 "operational strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080158 "Betriebsfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080158 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080158 pmdco:PMD_0000952)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080159 (weathering resistance)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/WeatheringResistance>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080159 "weathering resistance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080159 "Witterungsbeständigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080159 "Ability of a material to resist the effects of weathering, such as wind, rain, and sunlight."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080159 "Fähigkeit eines Materials, den Auswirkungen von Witterungseinflüssen wie Wind, Regen und Sonnenlicht standzuhalten."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080159 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'weathering resistance' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'operational strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080159 "weathering resistance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080159 "Witterungsbeständigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080159 "weather resistant"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080159 "wetterbeständig"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080159 "Was a subclass of 'Operational Strength';\n\nBut 'Operational Strength' does not appear to be Quality."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080159 "OperationalStrength(x) ← WeatheringResistance(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080159 "HDPE pipes show high weathering resistance, retaining mechanical properties after years of UV exposure"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080159 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080159 pmdco:PMD_0080158)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080160 (specific strength)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/SpecificStrength>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080160 "Specific strength is a strength quality of a material expressed as the ratio of a strength measure to its density, representing the material's load-bearing capacity per unit mass"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080160 "Spezifische Festigkeit ist eine Festigkeitsqualität eines Materials, ausgedrückt als Verhältnis einer Festigkeitsgröße zu seiner Dichte und repräsentiert die Tragfähigkeit des Materials je Masseneinheit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080160 "strength-to-weight ratio"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080160 "Festigkeit-Gewichts-Verhältnis"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080160 "spezifische Festigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080160 "specific strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080160 "Strength(x) ← SpecificStrength(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080160 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'specific strength' have not yet been formalized. Although specific strength is defined as a ratio of strength to density, a co-inherence axiom cannot uniquely identify this quality among all strength qualities of the same bearer. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'strength'."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080160 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080160 pmdco:PMD_0000952)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080161 (mechanical strength)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/MechanicalStrength>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080161 "Mechanical strength refers to a material's ability to resist applied load without failure or plastic deformation, characterized by stress and strain"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080161 "Festigkeit in der Mechanik von Materialien bezeichnet die Fähigkeit eines Materials, eine angewandte Last ohne Versagen oder plastische Verformung zu widerstehen. Innere Kräfte werden auf der Basis einer Einheit als Spannungen ausgedrückt und bewirken eine Verformung des Materials, bekannt als Dehnung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080161 "mechanical strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080161 "Festigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080161 "Strength(x) ← MechanicalStrength(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080161 "The mechanical strength of a fiber composite increases with fiber volume fraction up to an optimum value"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080161 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'mechanical strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080161 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080161 pmdco:PMD_0000952)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080162 (proof strength)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ProofStrength>

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080162 "proof strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080162 "Festigkeitsnachweis"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080162 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'proof strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'mechanical strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080162 "proof stress"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080162 "The Rp0.2 proof strength of stainless steel 316L is approximately 170 MPa"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080162 "MechanicalStrength(x) ← ProofStrength(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080162 "Die Dehngrenze bezieht sich auf die Spannung, die ein Material aushalten kann, bis eine geringe plastische Verformung auftritt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080162 "Proof strength refers to the stress a material can endure until exhibiting a small amount of plastic deformation"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080162 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080162 pmdco:PMD_0080161)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080159 (weathering resistance)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/WeatheringResistance>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080159 "weathering resistance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080159 "Witterungsbeständigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080159 "Ability of a material to resist the effects of weathering, such as wind, rain, and sunlight."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080159 "Fähigkeit eines Materials, den Auswirkungen von Witterungseinflüssen wie Wind, Regen und Sonnenlicht standzuhalten."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080159 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'weathering resistance' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'operational strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080159 "weathering resistance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080159 "Witterungsbeständigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080159 "weather resistant"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080159 "wetterbeständig"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080159 "Was a subclass of 'Operational Strength';\n\nBut 'Operational Strength' does not appear to be Quality."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080159 "OperationalStrength(x) ← WeatheringResistance(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080159 "HDPE pipes show high weathering resistance, retaining mechanical properties after years of UV exposure"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080159 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080159 pmdco:PMD_0000952)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080163 (fatigue strength)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/FatigueStrength>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080163 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'fatigue strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080163 "Ermüdungsfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080163 "fatigue strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080163 "Fatigue strength denotes a material's ability to resist fatigue or cyclic loading"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080163 "Ermüdungsfestigkeit bezeichnet die Fähigkeit eines Materials, Ermüdung oder zyklische Belastung zu widerstehen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080163 "Ermüdungsfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080163 "fatigue strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080163 "Strength(x) ← FatigueStrength(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080163 "The fatigue strength of steel at 10^7 cycles is approximately half its tensile strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080163 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080163 pmdco:PMD_0000952)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080164 (elasticity)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/Elasticity>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080164 "elasticity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080164 "Elastizität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080164 "Elastizität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080164 "elasticity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080164 "resilience"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080164 "elastic"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080164 "elastisch"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080164 "Widerstandsfähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080164 "Rubber exhibits high elasticity, recovering its original shape after 300 % elongation"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080164 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'elasticity' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080164 "Strength(x) ← Elasticity(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080164 "Elastizität ist die Fähigkeit eines Objekts oder Materials, nach Deformation seine normale Form wiederherzustellen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080164 "Elasticity is the ability of an object or material to resume its normal shape after deformation"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080164 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080164 pmdco:PMD_0000952)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080165 (bulk modulus)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/BulkModulus>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080165 "Water has a bulk modulus of 2.2 GPa, resisting compression under high hydrostatic pressure"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080165 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bulk_modulus>)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080165 "Bulk modulus is a measure of the resistance of a substance to bulk compression, defined as the ratio of infinitesimal pressure increase to relative volume decrease"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080165 "Der Volumenmodul ist ein Maß für den Widerstand einer Substanz gegenüber Massenkompression, definiert als das Verhältnis von verschwindend geringem Druckanstieg zur relativen Volumenabnahme"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080165 "Stiffness(x) ← BulkModulus(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080165 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'bulk modulus' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'stiffness'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bulk_modulus."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080165 "Kompressionsmodul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080165 "bulk modulus"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080165 "bulk modulus"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080165 "Kompressionsmodul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080165 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080165 pmdco:PMD_0000949)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080166 (shear modulus)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ShearModulus>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080166 "Stiffness(x) ← ShearModulus(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080166 "Shear modulus is a measure of elastic shear stiffness, defined as the ratio of shear stress to shear strain"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080166 "Schubmodul ist ein Maß für die elastische Schersteifigkeit, definiert als Verhältnis von Schubspannung zu Scherdehnung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080166 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shear_modulus>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080166 "shear modulus"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080166 "Schubmodul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080166 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'shear modulus' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'stiffness'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shear_modulus."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080166 "The shear modulus of aluminum is 26 GPa, governing torsional deformation of shafts"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080166 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080166 pmdco:PMD_0000949)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080167 (specific elastic modulus)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/SpecificElasticModulus>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080167 "specific stiffness"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080167 "spezifischer Modul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080167 "specific modulus"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080167 "spezifische Steifigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080167 "Specific elastic modulus is a stiffness quality of a material expressed as the ratio of its elastic modulus to its density, representing the material's elastic stiffness per unit mass"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080167 "Spezifischer Elastizitätsmodul ist eine Steifigkeitsqualität eines Materials, ausgedrückt als Verhältnis seines Elastizitätsmoduls zu seiner Dichte und repräsentiert die elastische Steifigkeit des Materials je Masseneinheit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080167 "spezifischer Elastizitätsmodul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080167 "specific elastic modulus"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080167 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'specific elastic modulus' have not yet been formalized. Although specific elastic modulus is defined as a ratio of elastic modulus to density, a co-inherence axiom cannot uniquely identify this quality among all stiffness qualities of the same bearer. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'stiffness'."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080167 "Stiffness(x) ← SpecificElasticModulus(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080167 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080167 pmdco:PMD_0000949)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080168 (flexural modulus)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/FlexuralModulus>

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080168 "flexural modulus"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080168 "Biegemodul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080168 "bending modulus"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080168 "Stiffness(x) ← FlexuralModulus(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080168 "Biegemodul ist eine Steifigkeitsqualität eines Materials, die das Verhältnis von Spannung zu Dehnung im elastischen Bereich eines Biegeversuchs beschreibt und den Widerstand gegen elastische Verformung unter Biegebelastung repräsentiert"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080168 "Flexural modulus is a stiffness quality of a material that specifies the ratio of stress to strain in the elastic region of a bending test, representing resistance to elastic deformation under flexural load"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080168 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'flexural modulus' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'stiffness'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080168 "Flexural modulus of a glass-fibre reinforced polyamide measured as 9.5 GPa under ISO 178 three-point bending test conditions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080168 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080168 pmdco:PMD_0000949)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080169 (adhesion strength)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/AdhesionStrength>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080169 "Strength(x) ← AdhesionStrength(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080169 "Adhesion Strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080169 "Haftfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080169 "Adhesion strength measures the force required to separate two surfaces bonded together"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080169 "Haftfestigkeit ist das Maß für die Kraft, die erforderlich ist, um zwei miteinander verbundene Oberflächen zu trennen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080169 "Haftfestigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080169 "adhesion strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080169 "Adhesive Strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080169 "Klebkraft"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080169 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'adhesion strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080169 "An epoxy adhesive joint on steel substrates has an adhesion strength of 20 MPa in lap shear testing"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080169 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080169 pmdco:PMD_0000952)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080170 (plasticity)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/Plasticity>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080170 "Strength(x) ← Plasticity(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080170 "Low-carbon steel exhibits high plasticity, allowing deep drawing without cracking"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080170 "Plastizität bezeichnet die Fähigkeit eines Materials, dauerhafte Verformungen ohne Bruch oder Riss zu erleiden"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080170 "Plasticity signifies a material's ability to undergo permanent deformation without breaking or cracking"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080170 "Plastizität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080170 "plasticity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080170 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'plasticity' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080170 "plasticity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080170 "Plastizität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080170 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080170 pmdco:PMD_0000952)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080171 (yield strength)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/YieldStrength>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080171 "Yield strength signfies the stress level at which material begins to deform plastically, marking the end of elastic behavior"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080171 "Fließgrenze bezeichnet das Spannungsniveau, bei dem sich Material beginnt, plastisch zu verformen und das Ende des elastischen Verhaltens markiert"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080171 "Plasticity(x) ← YieldStrength(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080171 "Fließgrenze"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080171 "yield strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080171 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'yield strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'plasticity'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080171 "The yield strength of mild steel is approximately 250 MPa, beyond which permanent deformation begins"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080171 "yield stress"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080171 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080171 pmdco:PMD_0080170)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080172 (lower yield strength)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/LowerYieldStrength>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080172 "Lower yield strength defines the stress at which a material exhibits plastic behavior after initial yielding"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080172 "Untere Streckgrenze beschreibt die Spannung, bei der ein Material nach dem anfänglichen Fließen plastisches Verhalten zeigt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080172 "lower yield strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080172 "untere Streckgrenze"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080172 "untere Fließspannung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080172 "lower yield stress"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080172 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yield_(engineering)>)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080172 "The lower yield strength of mild steel is approximately 235 MPa, defining the onset of stable plastic flow"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080172 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'lower yield strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'yield strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yield_(engineering)."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080172 "YieldStrength(x) ← LowerYieldStrength(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080172 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080172 pmdco:PMD_0080171)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080173 (upper yield strength)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/UpperYieldStrength>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080173 "obere Fließspannung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080173 "upper yield stress"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080173 "Obere Streckgrenze charakterisiert die maximale Spannung, die vor dem plastischen Fließen eines Materials angewendet werden kann"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080173 "Upper yield strength characterizes the maximum stress that can be applied before a material begins to yield plastically"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080173 "YieldStrength(x) ← UpperYieldStrength(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080173 "obere Streckgrenze"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080173 "upper yield strength"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080173 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'upper yield strength' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'yield strength'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yield_(engineering)."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080173 "Mild steel exhibits an upper yield strength of about 300 MPa, followed by a yield drop to the lower yield point"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080173 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yield_(engineering)>)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080173 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080173 pmdco:PMD_0080171)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080174 (viscosity)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/Viscosity>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080174 "Viscosity measures a fluid's resistance to flow"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080174 "Viskosität misst den Widerstand eines Fluids gegen den Fluss"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080174 "viscosity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080174 "Viskosität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080174 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'viscosity' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'plasticity'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080174 "Plasticity(x) ← Viscosity(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080174 "viscosity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080174 "Viskosität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080174 "Honey at 25 C has a viscosity of about 10 Pa·s, flowing slowly under gravity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080174 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080174 pmdco:PMD_0080170)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080175 (extentional viscosity)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ExtentionalViscosity>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080175 "Die Dehnviskosität ist die Messung des Widerstands einer Flüssigkeit gegen den Fluss bei Dehnspannung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080175 "Extentional viscosity measures a fluid's resistance to tension flow"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080175 "Viscosity(x) ← ExtentionalViscosity(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080175 "Dehnviskosität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080175 "extentional viscosity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080175 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'extentional viscosity' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'viscosity'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080175 "A polymer melt shows an extensional viscosity three times its shear viscosity at low strain rates"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080175 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080175 pmdco:PMD_0080174)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080176 (shear viscosity)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ShearViscosity>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080176 "Shear viscosity measures a fluid's resistance to shear flow"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080176 "Scherviskosität misst den Widerstand eines Fluids gegen Scherfluss"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080176 "shear viscosity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080176 "Scherviskosität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080176 "Viscosity(x) ← ShearViscosity(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080176 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'shear viscosity' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'viscosity'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080176 "shear viscosity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080176 "Scherviskosität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080176 "The shear viscosity of glycerol at 25 C is about 1.5 Pa·s, much higher than water"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080176 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080176 pmdco:PMD_0080174)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080177 (kinematic viscosity)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/KinematicViscosity>

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080177 "kinematische Viskosität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080177 "kinematic viscosity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080177 "kinematic viscosity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080177 "kinematische Viskosität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080177 "kinetic viscosity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080177 "kinetische Viskosität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080177 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'kinematic viscosity' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'viscosity'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080177 "The kinematic viscosity of water at 20 C is about 1e-6 m2/s, used in pipe flow calculations"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080177 "Viscosity(x) ← KinematicViscosity(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080177 "Kinematic viscosity is the ratio of dynamic viscosity to density"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080177 "Die kinematische Viskosität ist das Verhältnis der dynamischen Viskosität zur Dichte"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080177 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080177 pmdco:PMD_0080174)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080178 (dynamic viscosity)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/DynamicViscosity>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080178 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'dynamic viscosity' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'viscosity'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080178 "Dynamic viscosity measures a fluid's resistance to gradual deformation by shear stress or tensile stress, indicative of the fluid's internal friction"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080178 "Die dynamische Viskosität ist ein Maß für den Widerstand eines Fluids gegen eine allmähliche Verformung durch Scher- oder Zugspannung. Es ist ein Maß für den inneren Widerstand des Fluids gegen den Fluss und kann als Maß für die Flüssigkeitsreibung betrachtet werden"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080178 "dynamische Viskosität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080178 "dynamic viscosity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080178 "Viscosity(x) ← DynamicViscosity(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080178 "dynamische Viskosität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080178 "dynamic viscosity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080178 "Motor oil at 40 C has a dynamic viscosity of about 100 mPa·s, resisting flow under shear"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080178 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080178 pmdco:PMD_0080174)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080179 (volume viscosity)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/VolumeViscosity>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080179 "Volume viscosity measures a fluid's resistance to volumetric stress"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080179 "Volumenviskosität misst den Widerstand eines Fluids gegenüber volumetrischer Belastung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080179 "Water has a volume viscosity of about 3 mPa·s at 25 C, relevant in acoustic wave propagation"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080179 "Viscosity(x) ← VolumeViscosity(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080179 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'volume viscosity' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'viscosity'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080179 "Volumenviskosität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080179 "volume viscosity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080179 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080179 pmdco:PMD_0080174)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080180 (brittleness)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/Brittleness>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080180 "Sprödigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080180 "brittleness"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080180 "MechanicalCapability(x) ← Brittleness(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080180 "Cast iron has high brittleness, fracturing without measurable plastic deformation under tensile loading"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080180 "Opposite to toughness, brittleness is the property of being easily broken or damaged"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080180 "Sprödigkeit ist die Eigenschaft, leicht zu brechen oder zu beschädigen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080180 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'brittleness' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'mechanical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080180 "Zerbrechlichkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080180 "fragility"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080180 "Sprödigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080180 "brittleness"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080180 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080180 pmdco:PMD_0080132)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080181 (ductility)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/Ductility>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080181 "Duktilität ist die Fähigkeit eines Materials, plastisch zu verformen, ohne zu brechen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080181 "Ductility is the ability of a material to deform plastically without breaking"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080181 "Duktilität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080181 "ductility"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080181 "flexibility"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080181 "Biegsamkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080181 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'ductility' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'mechanical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080181 "Duktilität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080181 "ductility"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080181 "MechanicalCapability(x) ← Ductility(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080181 "Low-carbon steel has high ductility, with elongation at break exceeding 30 %"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080181 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080181 pmdco:PMD_0080132)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080182 (malleability)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/Malleability>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080182 "Malleability refers to a material's amenability to forming by hammering or rolling, distinct from ductility"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080182 "Formbarkeit beschreibt Materialien, die durch Hammern oder Walzen bearbeitet werden können und sich von Duktilität unterscheiden"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080182 "Malleability"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080182 "Formbarkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080182 "Malleable"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080182 "formbar"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080182 "malleability"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080182 "Formbarkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080182 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'malleability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'ductility'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080182 "Ductility(x) ← Malleability(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080182 "Gold has high malleability, allowing it to be hammered into sheets less than 100 nm thick"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080182 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080182 pmdco:PMD_0080181)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080183 (load cell capacity)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/LoadCellCapacity>

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080183 "Kapazität der Wägezelle"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080183 "load cell capacity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080183 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'load cell capacity' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'mechanical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080183 "Kapazität der Wägezelle ist die Messung der maximalen Kraft, die eine Wägezelle genau ablesen kann"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080183 "Load cell capacity measures the maximum force a load cell can accurately read"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080183 "A tension-compression load cell has a load cell capacity of 50 kN for structural testing"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080183 "MechanicalCapability(x) ← LoadCellCapacity(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080183 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080183 pmdco:PMD_0080132)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080184 (resilience)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/Resilience>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080184 "Resilienzmodul"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080184 "modulus of resilience"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080184 "Elastizität ist die mechanische Fähigkeit eines Materials, bei elastischer Verformung Energie zu absorbieren und diese Energie bei Entlastung ohne bleibende Verformung abzugeben"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080184 "Resilience is a mechanical capability of a material to absorb energy when elastically deformed and release that energy upon unloading without permanent deformation"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080184 "Resilienz"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080184 "resilience"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080184 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'resilience' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'mechanical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080184 "MechanicalCapability(x) ← Resilience(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080184 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080184 pmdco:PMD_0080132)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080185 (optical capability)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/OpticalCapability>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080185 "Optische Fähigkeit beschreibt die Wechselwirkungen im Zusammenhang mit Licht, die über eine Entität stattfinden"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080185 "Optical capability describes interactions related to light occurring via an entity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080185 "optische Fähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080185 "optical capability"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080185 "PhysicalCapability(x) ← OpticalCapability(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080185 "A camera lens has an optical capability of resolving 100 line pairs per mm at the image plane"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080185 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'optical capability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080185 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080185 obo:BFO_0000016)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080186 (radiation reflection capability)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/RadiationReflectionCapability>

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080186 "radiation reflection capability"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080186 "Strahlungsreflexionsfähigkeiten"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080186 "Radiation reflection capability characterizes an entity's ability to reflect electromagnetic radiation"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080186 "Strahlungsreflexionsfähigkeit beschreibt die Fähigkeit einer Entität, elektromagnetische Strahlung zu reflektieren"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080186 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'radiation reflection capability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'optical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080186 "Polished aluminum foil has high radiation reflection capability, reflecting 90 % of infrared radiation"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080186 "OpticalCapability(x) ← RadiationReflectionCapability(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080186 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080186 pmdco:PMD_0080185)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080187 (radiation absorption capability)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/RadiationAbsorptionCapability>

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080187 "radiation absorption capability"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080187 "Strahlungsabsorptionsfähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080187 "Strahlungsabsorptionsfähigkeit beschreibt die Fähigkeit einer Entität, elektromagnetische Strahlung zu absorbieren"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080187 "Radiation absorption capability characterizes an entity's ability to absorb electromagnetic radiation"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080187 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'radiation absorption capability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'optical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080187 "Carbon black pigment has high radiation absorption capability, absorbing over 99 % of incident visible light"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080187 "OpticalCapability(x) ← RadiationAbsorptionCapability(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080187 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080187 pmdco:PMD_0080185)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080188 (radiation emitter)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/RadiationEmissionCapability>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080188 "Radiation emission capability refers to an entity's ability to emit light of a defined spectrum and intensity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080188 "Strahlungsemitter beschreibt die Fähigkeit einer Entität, Licht eines definierten Spektrums und Intensität zu emittieren"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080188 "OpticalCapability(x) ← RadiationEmissionCapability(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080188 "Strahlungsemitter"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080188 "radiation emitter"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080188 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'radiation emission capability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'optical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080188 "A cobalt-60 source is a radiation emitter used in industrial gamma-ray testing of welds"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080188 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080188 pmdco:PMD_0080185)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080189 (radiation transmission capability)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/RadiationTransmissionCapability>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080189 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'radiation transmission capability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'optical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080189 "A thin beryllium window has high radiation transmission capability for soft X-rays, passing over 90 % of flux"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080189 "Strahlungsübertragungsfähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080189 "radiation transmission capability"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080189 "Strahlungsübertragungsfähigkeit beschreibt die Fähigkeit einer Entität, elektromagnetische Strahlung zu übertragen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080189 "Radiation transmission capability describes an entity's ability to transmit electromagnetic radiation"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080189 "OpticalCapability(x) ← RadiationTransmissionCapability(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080189 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080189 pmdco:PMD_0080185)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080190 (thermal capability)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ThermalCapability>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080190 "Refractory bricks have a high thermal capability, withstanding furnace temperatures above 1600 C"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080190 "PhysicalCapability(x) ← ThermalCapability(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080190 "Thermische Fähigkeit kann durch eine Entität im Zusammenhang mit thermischer Wechselwirkung realisiert werden"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080190 "Thermal capability can be realized through an entity related to thermodynamic interaction"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080190 "thermische Fähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080190 "thermal capability"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080190 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'thermal capability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080190 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080190 obo:BFO_0000016)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080191 (thermal capacity)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ThermalCapacity>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080191 "Wärmekapazität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080191 "heat capacity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080191 "ThermalCapability(x) ← ThermalCapacity(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080191 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heat_capacity>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080191 "thermal capacity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080191 "thermische Kapazität"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080191 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'thermal capacity' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermal capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heat_capacity."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080191 "Wärmekapazität, auch als thermische Kapazität bekannt, ist die Menge an Wärme, die erforderlich ist, um eine Änderung der Temperatur eines Objekts um eine Einheit zu erzeugen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080191 "Thermal capacity, or heat capacity, is defined as the amount of heat required to produce a unit change in temperature of an object"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080191 "A steel block of 1 kg has a thermal capacity of 500 J/K, absorbing heat with moderate temperature rise"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080191 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080191 pmdco:PMD_0080190)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080192 (flammability)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/Flammability>

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080192 "Entflammbarkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080192 "flammability"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080192 "Entflammbarkeit ist eine thermische Fähigkeit eines Materials, die seine Fähigkeit beschreibt, bei Exposition gegenüber einer Flamme oder Wärmequelle unter festgelegten Bedingungen zu entzünden und die Verbrennung aufrechtzuerhalten"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080192 "Flammability is a thermal capability of a material that characterises its ability to ignite and sustain combustion when exposed to a flame or heat source under specified conditions"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080192 "combustibility"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080192 "Brennbarkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080192 "ThermalCapability(x) ← Flammability(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080192 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'flammability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermal capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080192 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080192 pmdco:PMD_0080190)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080193 (heating capability)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/HeatingCapability>

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080193 "heating capability"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080193 "Aufheizfähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080193 "Heating capability refers to a material artifact's ability to cause temperature increase in another material entity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080193 "Die Heizfähigkeit bezieht sich auf die Fähigkeit eines Materialartefakts, einen Temperaturanstieg in einem anderen Materialobjekt zu verursachen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080193 "An induction heater has a heating capability of 10 kW, raising a steel billet to 1200 C in 60 s"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080193 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'heating capability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermal capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080193 "ThermalCapability(x) ← HeatingCapability(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080193 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080193 pmdco:PMD_0080190)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080194 (thermal insulation)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ThermalInsulation>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080194 "Thermische Isolierung verringert den Wärmeaustausch zwischen Objekten, die in thermischem Kontakt oder Strahlungseinfluss stehen, realisiert durch spezielle Konstruktionsmethoden oder Materialien"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080194 "Thermal insulation reduces heat transfer between objects in thermal contact or radiative influence, achieved with engineered methods or material properties"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080194 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thermal_insulation>)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080194 "Glass wool with a thermal conductivity of 0.04 W/(m·K) provides effective thermal insulation in building walls"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080194 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'thermal insulation' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermal capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thermal_insulation."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080194 "thermische Isolierung"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080194 "thermal insulation"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080194 "ThermalCapability(x) ← ThermalInsulation(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080194 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080194 pmdco:PMD_0080190)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080195 (radiant energy)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/RadiantEnergy>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080195 "Strahlungsenergie bezieht sich auf die Energie elektromagnetischer Strahlung, die durch Integration des Strahlungsflusses über die Zeit berechnet wird"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080195 "Radiant energy refers to the energy of electromagnetic radiation, calculated by integrating radiant flux over time"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080195 "radiant energy"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080195 "Strahlungsenergie"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000119 pmdco:PMD_0080195 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Radiant_energy>)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080195 "A pulsed laser delivers 1 mJ of radiant energy per pulse to the workpiece surface"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080195 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'radiant energy' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermal capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Radiant_energy."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080195 "ThermalCapability(x) ← RadiantEnergy(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080195 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080195 pmdco:PMD_0080190)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080196 (thermal expansion coefficient)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ThermalExpansionCoefficient>

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080196 "thermischer Ausdehnungkoeffizient"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080196 "thermal expansion coefficient"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080196 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'thermal expansion coefficient' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermal capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080196 "Thermal expansion coefficient quantifies the degree to which a material expands upon heating, representing fractional change per degree temperature increase"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080196 "Thermischer Ausdehnungkoeffizient quantifiziert den Grad, in dem ein Material beim Erhitzen expandiert, und stellt die proportionale Änderung pro Temperaturanstieg dar"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080196 "The thermal expansion coefficient of borosilicate glass is 3.3e-6 per K, enabling thermal shock resistance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080196 "ThermalCapability(x) ← ThermalExpansionCoefficient(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080196 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080196 pmdco:PMD_0080190)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080197 (volumetric thermal expansion coefficient)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/VolumetricThermalExpansionCoefficient>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080197 "Liquid water near 4 C has a near-zero volumetric thermal expansion coefficient, giving maximum density"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080197 "volumetric thermal expansion coefficient"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080197 "thermischer Volumenausdehnungskoeffizient"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080197 "ThermalExpansionCoefficient(x) ← VolumetricThermalExpansionCoefficient(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080197 "Der volumetrische Wärmeausdehnungskoeffizient quantifiziert den Grad, um den sich ein Material beim gleichzeitigen Erhitzen in alle drei axialen Richtungen ausdehnt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080197 "Volumetric thermal expansion coefficient quantifies the degree to which a material expands upon heating into all three axial directions simultaneously"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080197 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'volumetric thermal expansion coefficient' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermal expansion coefficient'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080197 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080197 pmdco:PMD_0080196)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080198 (linear thermal expansion coefficient)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/LinearThermalExpansionCoefficient>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080198 "Aluminum has a linear thermal expansion coefficient of 23.1e-6 per K, causing notable dimensional changes during heating"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080198 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'linear thermal expansion coefficient' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermal expansion coefficient'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080198 "linearer thermischer Ausdehnungkoeffizient"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080198 "linear thermal expansion coefficient"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080198 "ThermalExpansionCoefficient(x) ← LinearThermalExpansionCoefficient(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080198 "Linear thermal expansion coefficient quantifies the degree to which a material expands upon heating into a specific axial direction"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080198 "Der lineare Wärmeausdehnungskoeffizient quantifiziert den Grad, um den sich ein Material beim Erhitzen in eine bestimmte axiale Richtung ausdehnt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080198 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080198 pmdco:PMD_0080196)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080199 (cooling capability)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/CoolingCapability>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080199 "A heat pipe cooling system has a cooling capability of 150 W at a junction temperature below 85 C"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080199 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'cooling capability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermal capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080199 "Die Kühlfähigkeit bezieht sich auf die Fähigkeit eines Materialartefakts, einen Temperaturabfall in einem anderen Materialgebilde zu verursachen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080199 "Cooling capability refers to a material artifact's ability to cause temperature decrease in another material entity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080199 "Abkühlfähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080199 "cooling capability"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080199 "ThermalCapability(x) ← CoolingCapability(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080199 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080199 pmdco:PMD_0080190)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080200 (flame resistance)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/FlameResistance>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080200 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'flame resistance' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermal capability', disjoint from 'flammability' as the inverse capability. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080200 "ThermalCapability(x) ← FlameResistance(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080200 "Flame resistance is a thermal capability of a material that characterises its ability to resist ignition and inhibit the spread of combustion when exposed to a flame or heat source"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080200 "Flammbeständigkeit ist eine thermische Fähigkeit eines Materials, die seine Fähigkeit beschreibt, einer Entzündung zu widerstehen und die Ausbreitung der Verbrennung bei Exposition gegenüber einer Flamme oder Wärmequelle zu verhindern"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080200 "Brandbeständigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080200 "fire resistance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080200 "flame resistance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080200 "Flammbeständigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080200 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080200 pmdco:PMD_0080190)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080201 (thermal conductance)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ThermalConductance>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080201 "A copper heat spreader of 2 mm thickness has a high thermal conductance, efficiently dissipating chip heat"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080201 "Thermische Leitung beschreibt den Prozess, bei dem Wärme vom heißeren zum kälteren Ende eines Objekts übertragen wird, gekennzeichnet durch Leitfähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080201 "Thermal conduction refers to the process by which heat is transferred from the hotter end to the colder end of an object, characterized by conductance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080201 "thermal conductance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080201 "thermische Leitfähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080201 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'thermal conductance' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermal capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080201 "ThermalCapability(x) ← ThermalConductance(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080201 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080201 pmdco:PMD_0080190)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080202 (thermal shock resistance)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/ThermalShockResistance>

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080202 "thermal shock resistance"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080202 "Thermoschockbeständigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080202 "Thermoschockbeständigkeit ist eine thermische Fähigkeit eines Materials, die seine Fähigkeit beschreibt, schnelle und große Temperaturänderungen ohne Rissbildung, Abplatzungen oder Verlust der mechanischen Integrität zu überstehen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080202 "Thermal shock resistance is a thermal capability of a material that characterises its ability to withstand rapid and large changes in temperature without cracking, spalling, or loss of mechanical integrity"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080202 "ThermalCapability(x) ← ThermalShockResistance(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel pmdco:PMD_0080202 "Temperaturwechselbeständigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080202 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'thermal shock resistance' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'thermal capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080202 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080202 pmdco:PMD_0080190)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080203 (radiation emission capability)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/RadiationEmissonCapability>

AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080203 "A tungsten filament at 2800 K has significant radiation emission capability, producing visible white light"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080203 "PhysicalCapability(x) ← RadiationEmissonCapability(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080203 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'radiation emission capability' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080203 "Strahlungsemissionsfähigkeit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080203 "radiation emission capability"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080203 "Radiation emission capability is a physical capability of a material entity to emit electromagnetic radiation, realized in processes where the bearer radiates energy in the form of electromagnetic waves"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080203 "Die Strahlungsemissionsfähigkeit ist die physikalische Fähigkeit eines materiellen Wesens, elektromagnetische Strahlung auszusenden, die in Prozessen realisiert wird, bei denen der Träger Energie in Form elektromagnetischer Wellen ausstrahlt"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080203 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080203 obo:BFO_0000016)

# Class: pmdco:PMD_0080204 (water absorption)
# Adopted from IOF: <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Physical/WaterAbsorption>

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080204 "PhysicalCapability(x) ← WaterAbsorption(x)"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 pmdco:PMD_0080204 "Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'water absorption' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'physical capability'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080204 "Wasseraufnahme ist eine physische Fähigkeit eines Materials, Wasser aufzunehmen, quantifiziert als Massenzunahme einer Probe im Verhältnis zur anfänglichen Trockenmasse"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 pmdco:PMD_0080204 "Water absorption is a physical capability of a material to take up water, quantified as the increase in mass of a specimen relative to its initial dry mass"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080204 "Wasseraufnahme"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pmdco:PMD_0080204 "water absorption"@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example pmdco:PMD_0080204 "Water absorption of a nylon 6 specimen immersed for 24 hours expressed as 2.5% of its dry mass, measured according to ISO 62."@en-US)
AnnotationAssertion(pmdco:PMD_0000060 pmdco:PMD_0080204 "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(pmdco:PMD_0080204 obo:BFO_0000016)

